<br>
Alan spent time gathering info on what the Mage class as a whole wanted to feel balanced.  We asked for a spell that made pets immune to AoE fear so we could use them on Dragons.  We got it.  We asked for pet SoW.  We got it.  We asked for pets not to eat one wave of our Rain spells.  We got it.  We asked for higher level pet heals.  We got two of them.  We asked for new pet graphics.  We got it (yeah they suck IMO but thats besides the point).  We asked for Improved Invis.  We got it.  We asked for an upgrade to the Mod Rod.  We got it.<br>
<br>
WE GOT MANY OF THE IMPORTANT THINGS WE ASKED FOR DURING THE CLASS BALANCING DISCUSSIONS!<br>
<br>
So I have to ask the question ... if our class is so screwed up, why didn't these other issues get mentioned on our class balancing talks?<br>
