I just think ppl forget how we have ALWAYS been with the uber mobs.. We really never did that much damage in the long run.. <br>
<br>
I not going to fight about this this was suppose to be a postive post.. I thought, and you jumped in attacking this guy for his lvls... thats why I got a little upset.<br>
<br>
What I have seen in the pass 2 years on this board is basically the same complaints about basically the same things.. If you go back up and read some of the things that we have got in the last year if not a little longer they have gave us some REALLY nice util spell to try to cover some of the problems we had.. Like feared pets pets not keeping up and summon companion spells..<br>
<br>
Yes some things suck about this class, but on the other hand there some really GREAT things about this class.. I feel we are balanced. <br>
